| 
| Meta-type of read-only variables, including routine parameter and the special variable
| 'Self'.
| 

class EL_READONLY_VARIABLE
    is_a EL_VARIABLE

feature_group ("access")

    | 
    | Variable definition to which this reference refers.
    | 
    prop definition: BMM_READONLY_VARIABLE;

    | 
    | Defined to return False in all cases.
    | 
    prop is_writable: Boolean;


end
